8</small>\n| [[1973 Richmond 500|RCH]]\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Carolina 500|CAR]]<br><small>25</small>\n| [[Southeastern 500|BRI]]\n| style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| ''[[1973 Atlanta 500|ATL]]''<br><small>11</small>\n| [[1973 Gwyn Staley 400|NWS]]\n| [[1973 Rebel 500|DAR]]\n| [[Virginia 500|MAR]]\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Winston 500 (Spring)|TAL]]<br><small>38</small>\n| [[Music City 420|NSV]]\n| [[1973 World 600|CLT]]\n| [[Mason-Dixon 500|DOV]]\n| [[1973 Alamo 500|TWS]]\n| [[1973 Tuborg 400|RSD]]\n| [[Motor State 400|MCH]]\n| style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[1973 Medal of Honor Firecracker 400|DAY]]<br><small>4</small>\n| [[Volunteer 500|BRI]]\n| [[1973 Dixie 500|ATL]]\n| [[Talladega 500 (Fall Race)|TAL]]\n| [[Nashville 420|NSV]]\n| [[1973 Southern 500|DAR]]\n| [[Capital City 500|RCH]]\n| [[Delaware 500|DOV]]\n| [[Wilkes 400|NWS]]\n| [[Old Dominion 500|MAR]]\n| [[1973 National 500|CLT]]\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[1973 American 500|CAR]]<br><small>25</small>\n| colspan=3|\n! NA\n! -\n! <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racing-reference.info/drivdet/johncgo01/1973/W|title=Gordon Johncock \u2013 1973 NASCAR Winston Cup Results|work=Racing-Reference|accessdate=April 16, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n! [[1975 NASCAR Winston Cup Series|1975]]\n! [[Ellington Racing]]\n! 28\n! [[Chevrolet|Chevy]]\n| [[1975 Winston Western 500|RSD]]\n| [[1975 Daytona 500|DAY]]\n| [[Richmond 500|RCH]]\n| [[Carolina 500|CAR]]\n| [[Southeastern 500|BRI]]\n| [[Atlanta 500|ATL]]\n| [[Gwyn Staley 400|NWS]]\n| [[Rebel 500|DAR]]\n| [[Virginia 500|MAR]]\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[1975 Winston 500|TAL]]<br><small>36</small>\n| [[1975 Music City USA 420|NSV]]\n| [[Mason-Dixon 500|DOV]]\n| [[1975 World 600|CLT]]\n| [[Tuborg 400|RSD]]\n| [[Motor State 400|MCH]]\n| [[Firecracker 400|DAY]]\n| [[Nashville 420|NSV]]\n| [[Purolator 500 (Pocono)|POC]]\n| [[Talladega 500 (Fall Race)|TAL]]\n| [[1975 Champion Spark Plug 400|MCH]]\n| [[Southern 500|DAR]]\n| [[Delaware 500|DOV]]\n| [[Wilkes 400|NWS]]\n| [[Old Dominion 500|MAR]]\n| [[1975 National 500|CLT]]\n| [[Capital City 500|RCH]]\n| [[American 500|CAR]]\n| [[Volunteer 500|BRI]]\n| [[Dixie 500|ATL]]\n| [[1975 Los Angeles Times 500|ONT]]\n| \n! NA\n! -\n! <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racing-reference.info/drivdet/johncgo01/1975/W|title=Gordon Johncock \u2013 1975 NASCAR Winston Cup Results|work=Racing-Reference|accessdate=April 16, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n! [[1976 NASCAR Winston Cup Series|1976]]\n! [[K&K Insurance Racing]]\n! 17\n! [[Dodge]]\n| [[Winston Western 500|RSD]]\n| [[1976 Daytona 500|DAY]]\n| [[Carolina 500|CAR]]\n| [[Richmond 400|RCH]]\n| [[Southeastern 500|BRI]]\n| [[Atlanta 500|ATL]]\n| [[1976 Gwyn Staley 400|NWS]]\n| [[Rebel 500|DAR]]\n| [[Virginia 500|MAR]]\n| [[1976 Winston 500|TAL]]\n| [[1976 Music City USA 420|NSV]]\n| [[1976 Mason-Dixon 500|DOV]]\n| [[1976 World 600|CLT]]\n| [[1976 Riverside 400|RSD]]\n| [[1976 Cam 2 Motor Oil 400|MCH]]\n| [[1976 Firecracker 400|DAY]]\n| [[Nashville 420|NSV]]\n| [[Purolator 500 (Pocono)|POC]]\n| [[Talladega 500 (Fall Race)|TAL]]\n| [[Champion Spark Plug 400|MCH]]\n| [[1976 Volunteer 400|BRI]]\n| [[1976 Southern 500|DAR]]\n| [[Capital City 400|RCH]]\n| [[Delaware 500|DOV]]\n| [[Old Dominion 500|MAR]]\n| [[Wilkes 400|NWS]]\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[1976 National 500|CLT]]<br><small>39</small>\n| [[1976 American 500|CAR]]\n| [[1976 Dixie 500|ATL]]\n| [[1976 Los Angeles Times 500|ONT]]\n| \n! NA\n! -\n! <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racing-reference.info/drivdet/johncgo01/1976/W|title=Gordon Johncock \u2013 1976 NASCAR Winston Cup Results|work=Racing-Reference|accessdate=April 16, 2017}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=====Daytona 500=====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 90%;\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Team\n! Manufacturer\n! Start\n! Finish\n|-\n| [[1966 Daytona 500|1966]]\n| [[K&K Insurance Racing]]\n| [[Dodge]]\n|align=center| 13\n|align=center style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| 29\n|-\n| [[1967 Daytona 500|1967]]\n| [[R.L. Diestler]]\n| [[Plymouth (automobile